data.description: Premium location , five minutes away from turnpike. The Tides is located within the prestigious and well maintained Isles at Bayshore. FULLY remodeled two stories single family house with a beautiful and modern remodeled kitchen, zebra blinds and elegant curtains, laminated floors in both stories. A very quite neighborhood family oriented , house in impecable shape constructed in 2012. Conveniently located really closed to the Black Point Marina. Many amenities full of entertainment, gym and a huge pool accompanied of a couple jacuzzis.
